OL,5, A growing number of UK businesses are  
OL,6, at risk of going under, as costs spiral
OL,7, and Covid loan repayments come due, a  
OL,8, report has found.                      
OL,10,FConstruction and hospitality are the   
OL,11,Fsectors struggling most, according to  
OL,12,Finsolvency firm Begbies Traynor.       
OL,14,FLoan repayment schedules should be     
OL,15,Fextended to ease the pressure, it said.
OL,17,FThe government said it had given       
OL,18,Fbusinesses an "unprecedented package of
OL,19,Fsupport" and increased flexibility in  
OL,20,Fpaying back Covid loans.               
